#: ../../../release/dev/implicit-find-events.rst:2
msgid "implicit-find-events"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../release/dev/implicit-find-events.rst:4
msgid ""
"The :manual:`cmake-configure-log(7)` will report events from ``find_`` "
"commands without any find-debug flags (e.g., :variable:"
"`CMAKE_FIND_DEBUG_MODE`) when they transition between \"found\" and \"not "
"found\" or when they are first defined. The :variable:"
"`CMAKE_FIND_DEBUG_MODE_NO_IMPLICIT_CONFIGURE_LOG` variable will suppress "
"these events without any explicit request for a debug mode."
msgstr ""
